Wire the cs4237b/ sub-directory into sound/isa/Makefile.

Single-line addition: a per-CONFIG obj-y assignment so that the new
sub-directory is descended into only when CONFIG_SND_CS4237B is
selected (=m or =y). The existing CONFIG_SND-driven directory list
is left untouched.

Generated against Linux v6.18.8.

--- a/sound/isa/Makefile
+++ b/sound/isa/Makefile
@@ -22,5 +22,7 @@ obj-$(CONFIG_SND_OPL3SA2) += snd-opl3sa2.o
 obj-$(CONFIG_SND_SC6000) += snd-sc6000.o
 obj-$(CONFIG_SND_SSCAPE) += snd-sscape.o

+obj-$(CONFIG_SND_CS4237B) += cs4237b/
+
 obj-$(CONFIG_SND) += ad1816a/ ad1848/ cs423x/ es1688/ galaxy/ gus/ msnd/ opti9xx/ \
 		     sb/ wavefront/ wss/
